# Admin form pattern (эталон)

Reference implementation: `admin/components/category-groups-editor.js` + `admin/utils/admin-form.js`.

## Stack

```html
<div class="admin-form-stack">
  <div class="admin-field-block">…</div>
</div>
```

- `admin-form-stack`: `flex flex-col`, `gap: 20px` (`space-y-5`), `width: 100%` — **no max-width**
- No ad-hoc `margin-y` / `padding-y` between blocks inside the stack

## Labels

Always `admin-field-label` (11px, bold, uppercase, muted, `margin-bottom: 6px`):

```html
<label class="admin-field-label" for="…">Название</label>
```

Aliases in CSS: `avr-field-label`, `cgr-field-label`, `mkb-field-label`.

## Inputs / selects

- Primary fields: `admin-field-input` — **h-10 (40px)**, `w-full`, `rounded-lg` (`--radius-sm`)
- Textareas: `admin-field-textarea` — `w-full`, min-height ~80px
- Footer right edge must align with field right edge → same horizontal padding on `.avr-detail-scroll` and `.avr-detail-foot` (`var(--space-lg)`)

## Channel + order (when entity has web/kiosk)

Use `renderChannelAvailabilityGrid()` from `admin/utils/admin-form.js`:

```html
<div class="admin-channel-grid"> <!-- grid: 1fr 140px 140px, items-end, w-full -->
```

Left: segmented control `admin-channel-tabs admin-channel-tabs--h10`. Right: two order inputs (groups only — pass `showOrderFields: false` for promos/banners).

**Left sidebar list cards** (master list): see **Admin sidebar list card** in `.cursor/rules/design-system.mdc` — same row markup, W/K badges, schedule status, deprioritized divider for all entity editors.

## Media upload row

```html
<div class="admin-media-row">
  <!-- preview -->
  <!-- button h-9 -->
  <p class="admin-media-path">/path</p> <!-- text-xs, muted, ml-4 from button -->
</div>
```

## Toolbar buttons inside blocks

Use `products-create-btn` (h-9 compact), not full-width outline giants.

## Footers

`avr-detail-foot` → `avr-detail-foot-row` + `footer-action-bar`. Match scroll horizontal padding.

**Отменить:** `bindAvrDetailCancel(root, buttonId, { isDirty, discard, save?, onClose })` — `onClose` сбрасывает `selectedId` в `null` и показывает empty-state. Не использовать `if (!isDirty()) return` без закрытия панели.
